Empty-pages.content:
Page for notes that have little to no content and need to be filled. Use backlink to identify pages and fill them out if possible.
It is possible that the page itself is empty, but the page linking to it has some contents that are available
const pages = dv.current().file.inlinks;
if (pages.length === 0) {
  dv.paragraph(&quot;No backlinks.&quot;);
} else {
  dv.list(pages.map(p =&gt; dv.fileLink(p.path)));
}

Unfamiliar-techniques.content:
const pages = dv.current().file.inlinks;
if (pages.length === 0) {
  dv.paragraph(&quot;No backlinks.&quot;);
} else {
  dv.list(pages.map(p =&gt; p.path));
}
const unresolved = new Set();

for (let page of dv.pages()) {
  const links = page.file.outlinks;
  for (let link of links) {
    if (!dv.page(link.path)) {
      unresolved.add(link.path);
    }
  }
}

dv.table([&quot;Uncreated Pages&quot;], Array.from(unresolved).map(p =&gt; [dv.fileLink(p)]));
